events.text:
It doesn't seem like you understand.
I am the ruler of this world.
You don't belong here. Have I not made it clear you gain nothing from challening me?
What do you repeat yourself so much for?
Don't answer. It doesn't matter.
You have repeatedly broke the balance of this world.
How did you even get here? I haven't seen your actual dream self in ages.
I've been trying to fix this situation by getting her back here, you know.
But if that won't suffice, I can stop you from dreaming entirely.
And you leave me no other choice.
Good night.
